The team from the Serious Commercial Crime Unit of the Hawks arrested a fugitive tax swindler suspect at his hideout near Strandfontein following investigations.Abdul Karriem Wiener (56) appeared briefly at the Bellville Magistrate s Court after he was arrested for fraud.Weiner was remanded in custody for bail information and the matter has been adjourned until September 4.He allegedly defrauded the PageSouth African Receiver of Revenue (SARS) during the period between 2014 and 2015 and submitted fraudulent income tax returns and received payments totalling approximately R600 000-00 as a result. He is facing charges of fraud.&nbsp;